## Project Structure

```
binary-analyzer/
├── src/
│   └── binary_analyzer/
│       ├── __init__.py          # public API exports
│       ├── __main__.py          # python -m binary_analyzer entry
│       ├── cli.py               # argument parsing, human-readable output, main()
│       ├── analysis.py          # build_results(), detect_file_type()
│       ├── indicators.py        # get_imports(), scoring, string matching
│       ├── entropy.py           # Shannon entropy + verdict
│       ├── pe_parser.py         # manual PE header parser (sections, arch)
│       ├── string_extractor.py  # printable string extraction
│       ├── risk.py              # classify_risk_level(), risk ranking
│       ├── quarantine.py        # isolate, restore, delete, manifest, CSV
│       ├── rules.py             # AnalysisRules, JSON loading, merging
│       └── default_rules.json   # bundled default detection rules
├── tests/
│   ├── conftest.py
│   ├── test_analysis.py
│   ├── test_cli.py
│   ├── test_quarantine.py
│   ├── test_risk.py
│   └── test_rules.py
├── samples/                     # sample binaries for quick testing
├── test-sample/                 # synthetic benign + suspicious samples
├── .github/
│   └── workflows/
│       ├── tests.yml            # CI: run pytest on push/PR
│       └── build.yml            # CI: build Windows + Linux binaries
├── build.py                     # cross-platform PyInstaller build script
├── build.bat                    # Windows build wrapper
├── build.sh                     # Linux build wrapper
├── pyproject.toml               # package metadata, deps, entry points
└── README.md
```
